    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551590/extras/0c21372967ad1eeab37da989fcbdc816.avif?t=1749283263\" width=616 height=72 /></span>政治家艾利奥与他的妻子洛蕾塔过着幸福又和平的生活。但在艾利奥升职为党内纸媒的主编后，新主笔法布罗加入了。法布罗的加入并非为了助艾利奥一臂之力——恰恰相反，他盯上了艾利奥的位置。法布罗无一不备，愿为此付出任何代价——哪怕是让洛蕾塔成为他手中的一颗棋子。洛蕾塔作为艾利奥秘书的新工作还顺利吗？艾利奥能够挫败法布罗的邪恶计划吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551590/extras/5740eba2fdd0cd5e2cc63632b68634d7.avif?t=1749283263\" width=616 height=73 /></span>故事发生在一个20世纪背景的美丽小镇，请随意探索街道并与居民交谈吧！艾利奥必须阻止法布罗的邪恶计划——调查小镇，从同胞们手中发掘碎片寻求真相！体验传统的日常生活RPG的同时，别忘了揭露法布罗谎言背后的真相。阻止法布罗，赢得本场守擂战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551590/extras/5991f7a5f7c6038b793a5007ad6b09a2.avif?t=1749283263\" width=616 height=73 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551590/extras/c48b99de535f94a955bc14b6c4690b6b.avif?t=1749283263\" width=616 height=275 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551590/extras/842673dc95b7e921859f6ab92e351fe6.avif?t=1749283263\" width=616 height=275 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551590/extras/294d7aee79cd1fa9c1f2c65095ffc32e.avif?t=1749283263\" width=616 height=275 /></span></p>",
